text: Ogün Altıparmak (10 November 1938 – 2 February 2025) was a Turkish footballer. He played for the Turkey national football team from 1961 to 1968, making thirty-two appearances. Altıparmak died on 2 February 2025, at the age of 86.Fenerbahçe efsanesini kaybetti: 'İlk gol kralı' 86 yaşında vefat etti ==References== Category:1938 births Category:2025 deaths Category:Turkish footballers
